.TH UNHINGED-VOICE 1 "November 2025" "Unhinged" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
unhinged-voice \- Text-to-speech voice generation for Unhinged platform

.SH SYNOPSIS
.B unhinged voice generate
\fITEXT\fR [\fIOPTIONS\fR]

.SH DESCRIPTION
The
.B unhinged voice
command provides text-to-speech voice generation with multiple voice options.
Designed to be layered with GTK4 UI later, this command works standalone
for scripting and automation.

.SH SUBCOMMANDS

.SS VOICE GENERATION
.B unhinged voice generate
\fITEXT\fR [\fIOPTIONS\fR]

Generate voice/audio from text using TTS engine.

.B Voice Generation Options:
.RS
.TP
.B -v, --voice \fIVOICE\fR
Voice to use: nova, echo, sage, shimmer (default: nova)
.TP
.B --speed \fISPEED\fR
Speech speed 0.5-2.0 (default: 1.0)
.TP
.B -e, --emotion \fIEMOTION\fR
Emotion/tone: neutral, happy, sad, angry (default: neutral)
.TP
.B -o, --output \fIPATH\fR
Save audio to file (default: stdout path)
.TP
.B -f, --file \fIPATH\fR
Read text from file instead of argument
.RE

.SH VOICE DESCRIPTIONS

.TP
.B nova
Female voice, American accent, natural speed
.TP
.B echo
Male voice, American accent, natural speed
.TP
.B sage
Male voice, American accent, slightly slower
.TP
.B shimmer
Female voice, British accent, natural speed

.SH EXAMPLES

Generate voice with default settings:
.RS
.B unhinged voice generate "Hello world"
.RE

Generate with different voice:
.RS
.B unhinged voice generate "Hello world" -v echo
.RE

Generate with faster speech:
.RS
.B unhinged voice generate "Hello world" --speed 1.5
.RE

Generate with emotion:
.RS
.B unhinged voice generate "I love this!" -e happy
.RE

Save audio to file:
.RS
.B unhinged voice generate "Hello world" -o greeting.mp3
.RE

Read text from file:
.RS
.B unhinged voice generate -f script.txt
.RE

Pipe text from stdin:
.RS
.B echo "Hello world" | unhinged voice generate
.RE

.SH OUTPUT

Generated audio files are saved to:
.RS
.B /build/tmp/generated/
.RE

Audio format: MP3 (default)
Sample rate: 24000 Hz

.SH SPEED SETTINGS

.TP
.B 0.5x
Very slow, good for emphasis
.TP
.B 1.0x
Normal speed (default)
.TP
.B 1.5x
Fast, good for quick delivery
.TP
.B 2.0x
Very fast, maximum speed

.SH EMOTION SETTINGS

.TP
.B neutral
Standard, professional tone
.TP
.B happy
Upbeat, enthusiastic tone
.TP
.B sad
Somber, melancholic tone
.TP
.B angry
Intense, forceful tone

